s://v0.wordpress.com/player.swf?v=1.04&guid=P8q7dcHc&isDynamicSeeking=true\";s:5:\"width\";s:3:\"400\";s:6:\"height\";s:3:\"266\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}}}}}i:5;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:121:\"\n		\n		\n				\n				\n		\n				\n		\n\n		\n				\n								\n							\n		\n						\n\n\n		\n		\n\n		\n\n		\n\n		\n\n		\n\n		\n\n		\n\n		\n\n		\n\n		\n\n		\n\n		\n\n		\n	\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:6:{s:0:\"\";a:8:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:49:\"Designing Themes with Gutenberg Blocks and Sketch\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:87:\"https://themeshaper.com/2018/03/07/designing-gutenberg-block-driven-themes-with-sketch/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:96:\"https://themeshaper.com/2018/03/07/designing-gutenberg-block-driven-themes-with-sketch/#comments\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"pubDate\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:31:\"Wed, 07 Mar 2018 14:24:44 +0000\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"category\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:17:\"Theme Development\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:9:\"Gutenberg\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"guid\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:30:\"http://themeshaper.com/?p=7015\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:11:\"isPermaLink\";s:5:\"false\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:11:\"description\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:115:\"Follow Kjell Reigstad’s process as he explores designing a block-driven theme with Sketch, for the Gutenberg era.\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:9:\"enclosure\";a:2:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:3:\"url\";s:74:\"https://videos.files.wordpress.com/3J8YCbg5/gutenberg-sketch-layout_hd.mp4\";s:6:\"length\";s:8:\"10112000\";s:4:\"type\";s:9:\"video/mp4\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}i:1;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:3:{s:3:\"url\";s:77:\"https://videos.files.wordpress.com/Uu1HxLuE/gutenberg-sketch-customize_hd.mp4\";s:6:\"length\";s:7:\"4853760\";s:4:\"type\";s:9:\"video/mp4\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Kjell Reigstad\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:20184:\"<p>There’s been an exciting <a href=\"https://themeshaper.com/2017/11/10/the-promise-of-gutenberg-themes-as-more-design-less-baggage/\">discussion</a> happening around the changes that <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/gutenberg/\">Gutenberg</a> will bring to themes. At Automattic, we’ve begun to prepare for Gutenberg by reevaluating our theme design and development processes.</p>\n<p>As part of that work, I did some thinking about how I might start designing a block-driven theme today and what sorts of resources I&#8217;d want to have. The most important thing that came to mind was a way to access and customize all of the core Gutenberg blocks with a few clicks. This would allow me to quickly test and iterate on block design without having to dig into code. I do a good deal of my design work in <a href=\"https://www.sketchapp.com\">Sketch</a>, so I began to search for a way to make this possible there.</p>\n<p>Luckily, there are already a few Gutenberg-related Sketch files in the wild. The <a href=\"https://github.com/WordPress/gutenberg/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md\">Gutenberg Contributors page</a> on GitHub and the <a href=\"https://wordpress.org/gutenberg/handbook/reference/design-principles/#more-resources\">Design Principles &amp; Vision page</a> on WordPress.org are great places to start. These are mostly aimed at the Gutenberg editing interface, however, and didn&#8217;t quite accomplish what I was looking for, so I ended up building a new file instead:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/gutenberg-sketch-file.jpg\"><img data-attachment-id=\"7016\" data-permalink=\"https://themeshaper.com/2018/03/07/designing-gutenberg-block-driven-themes-with-sketch/gutenberg-sketch-file/\" data-orig-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/gutenberg-sketch-file.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"2260,900\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Gutenberg-Sketch-File\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/gutenberg-sketch-file.jpg?w=300\" data-large-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/gutenberg-sketch-file.jpg?w=840\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-7016\" style=\"border:1px solid #ccc;\" src=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/gutenberg-sketch-file.jpg?w=840\" alt=\"Gutenberg-Sketch-File.jpg\" srcset=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/gutenberg-sketch-file.jpg?w=840 840w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/gutenberg-sketch-file.jpg?w=1680 1680w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/gutenberg-sketch-file.jpg?w=150 150w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/gutenberg-sketch-file.jpg?w=300 300w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/gutenberg-sketch-file.jpg?w=768 768w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/gutenberg-sketch-file.jpg?w=1024 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 709px) 85vw, (max-width: 909px) 67vw, (max-width: 1362px) 62vw, 840px\"   /></a></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight:400;\">This new Sketch file contains <a href=\"https://sketchapp.com/docs/symbols/\">symbols</a> for all of the default Gutenberg blocks (with the exception of all the embeds, since those aren&#8217;t very customizable). With this set of symbols, it’s possible to quickly build a layout composed entirely of Gutenberg blocks using Sketch:</span></p>\n<p><div id=\"v-3J8YCbg5-1\" class=\"video-player\" style=\"width:840px;height:512px\">\n<embed id=\"v-3J8YCbg5-1-video\" src=\"https://v0.wordpress.com/player.swf?v=1.04&amp;guid=3J8YCbg5&amp;isDynamicSeeking=true\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" width=\"840\" height=\"512\" title=\"Gutenberg-Sketch-Layout\" wmode=\"direct\" seamlesstabbing=\"true\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" allowscriptaccess=\"always\" overstretch=\"true\"></embed></div></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight:400;\">It’s actually pretty fun to use! In a way, it’s Gutenberg — but for Sketch. <img src=\"https://s0.wp.com/wp-content/mu-plugins/wpcom-smileys/twemoji/2/72x72/1f604.png\" alt=\"?\" class=\"wp-smiley\" style=\"height: 1em; max-height: 1em;\" /><br />\n</span><span style=\"font-weight:400;\">From here, it&#8217;s easy to start customizing styles:</span></p>\n<p><div id=\"v-Uu1HxLuE-1\" class=\"video-player\" style=\"width:840px;height:512px\">\n<embed id=\"v-Uu1HxLuE-1-video\" src=\"https://v0.wordpress.com/player.swf?v=1.04&amp;guid=Uu1HxLuE&amp;isDynamicSeeking=true\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" width=\"840\" height=\"512\" title=\"Gutenberg-Sketch-Customize\" wmode=\"direct\" seamlesstabbing=\"true\" allowfullscreen=\"true\" allowscriptaccess=\"always\" overstretch=\"true\"></embed></div></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight:400;\">I took this method for a spin and tried to mock up a theme for an imagined restaurant. To get started, I built out the page structure using default Gutenberg blocks:</span></p>\n<p>\n<a href=\'https://themeshaper.com/2018/03/07/designing-gutenberg-block-driven-themes-with-sketch/restaurant-r1-mobile-2/\'><img width=\"18\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/restaurant-r1-mobile1.png?w=18&#038;h=150\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/restaurant-r1-mobile1.png?w=18 18w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/restaurant-r1-mobile1.png?w=36 36w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 18px) 85vw, 18px\" data-attachment-id=\"7038\" data-permalink=\"https://themeshaper.com/2018/03/07/designing-gutenberg-block-driven-themes-with-sketch/restaurant-r1-mobile-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/restaurant-r1-mobile1.png\" data-orig-size=\"375,3089\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Restaurant-R1-Mobile\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/restaurant-r1-mobile1.png?w=36\" data-large-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/restaurant-r1-mobile1.png?w=124\" /></a>\n<a href=\'https://themeshaper.com/2018/03/07/designing-gutenberg-block-driven-themes-with-sketch/restaurant-r1-desktop/\'><img width=\"50\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/restaurant-r1-desktop.png?w=50&#038;h=150\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/restaurant-r1-desktop.png?w=50 50w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/restaurant-r1-desktop.png?w=100 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 50px) 85vw, 50px\" data-attachment-id=\"7017\" data-permalink=\"https://themeshaper.com/2018/03/07/designing-gutenberg-block-driven-themes-with-sketch/restaurant-r1-desktop/\" data-orig-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/restaurant-r1-desktop.png\" data-orig-size=\"1020,3089\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Restaurant-R1-Desktop\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/restaurant-r1-desktop.png?w=99\" data-large-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/restaurant-r1-desktop.png?w=338\" /></a>\n</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight:400;\">From there, I started doing some light customizing. I cut myself off after a while, but the end result looked fairly decent:</span></p>\n<p>\n<a href=\'https://themeshaper.com/2018/03/07/designing-gutenberg-block-driven-themes-with-sketch/restaurant-r2-mobile/\'><img width=\"18\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/restaurant-r2-mobile.png?w=18&#038;h=150\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/restaurant-r2-mobile.png?w=18 18w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/restaurant-r2-mobile.png?w=36 36w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 18px) 85vw, 18px\" data-attachment-id=\"7020\" data-permalink=\"https://themeshaper.com/2018/03/07/designing-gutenberg-block-driven-themes-with-sketch/restaurant-r2-mobile/\" data-orig-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/restaurant-r2-mobile.png\" data-orig-size=\"375,3089\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Restaurant-R2-Mobile\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/restaurant-r2-mobile.png?w=36\" data-large-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/restaurant-r2-mobile.png?w=124\" /></a>\n<a href=\'https://themeshaper.com/2018/03/07/designing-gutenberg-block-driven-themes-with-sketch/restaurant-r2-desktop/\'><img width=\"50\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/restaurant-r2-desktop.png?w=50&#038;h=150\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/restaurant-r2-desktop.png?w=50 50w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/restaurant-r2-desktop.png?w=100 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 50px) 85vw, 50px\" data-attachment-id=\"7019\" data-permalink=\"https://themeshaper.com/2018/03/07/designing-gutenberg-block-driven-themes-with-sketch/restaurant-r2-desktop/\" data-orig-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/restaurant-r2-desktop.png\" data-orig-size=\"1020,3089\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Restaurant-R2-Desktop\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/restaurant-r2-desktop.png?w=99\" data-large-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/restaurant-r2-desktop.png?w=338\" /></a>\n</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight:400;\">I find this pretty cool. It’s an example of what a block-driven theme might look like with just a little bit of CSS customization. </span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight:400;\">From here, I could easily keep going and put together a complete, modular design system for this theme by customizing the rest of the Gutenberg blocks. I could view the blocks all at once on the Symbols page, and quickly build out a wide variety of layout options to make sure my styles held up to intense layout customization.</span></p>\n<hr />\n<p>I almost ended there, but I decided to confront a lingering concern I’ve had about Gutenberg: I’ve feared that if we lean too much on Gutenberg for theme layout, we&#8217;ll end up with lots of very similar, &#8220;blocky&#8221; themes. The restaurant site I designed above looks fine, but it&#8217;s also clearly made of blocks. I wondered if it’d be possible to create something more experimental using this same Sketch file as a base.</p>\n<p>So I took another stab at a pretend site design (this time for a band named Superserious), and forced myself to break out of the blocks a little more. Again, I began with a pure-Gutenberg layout:</p>\n<p>\n<a href=\'https://themeshaper.com/2018/03/07/designing-gutenberg-block-driven-themes-with-sketch/music-r1-mobile/\'><img width=\"18\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/music-r1-mobile.png?w=18&#038;h=150\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/music-r1-mobile.png?w=18 18w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/music-r1-mobile.png?w=36 36w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 18px) 85vw, 18px\" data-attachment-id=\"7022\" data-permalink=\"https://themeshaper.com/2018/03/07/designing-gutenberg-block-driven-themes-with-sketch/music-r1-mobile/\" data-orig-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/music-r1-mobile.png\" data-orig-size=\"375,3089\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Music-R1-Mobile\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/music-r1-mobile.png?w=36\" data-large-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/music-r1-mobile.png?w=124\" /></a>\n<a href=\'https://themeshaper.com/2018/03/07/designing-gutenberg-block-driven-themes-with-sketch/music-r1-desktop/\'><img width=\"50\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/music-r1-desktop.png?w=50&#038;h=150\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/music-r1-desktop.png?w=50 50w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/music-r1-desktop.png?w=100 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 50px) 85vw, 50px\" data-attachment-id=\"7021\" data-permalink=\"https://themeshaper.com/2018/03/07/designing-gutenberg-block-driven-themes-with-sketch/music-r1-desktop/\" data-orig-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/music-r1-desktop.png\" data-orig-size=\"1020,3089\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Music-R1-Desktop\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/music-r1-desktop.png?w=99\" data-large-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/music-r1-desktop.png?w=338\" /></a>\n</p>\n<p>But this time, I was much more aggressive in my customization and aimed for a more tailored mobile experience with bold typography:</p>\n<p>\n<a href=\'https://themeshaper.com/2018/03/07/designing-gutenberg-block-driven-themes-with-sketch/music-r2-mobile/\'><img width=\"18\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/music-r2-mobile.png?w=18&#038;h=150\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/music-r2-mobile.png?w=18 18w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/music-r2-mobile.png?w=36 36w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 18px) 85vw, 18px\" data-attachment-id=\"7024\" data-permalink=\"https://themeshaper.com/2018/03/07/designing-gutenberg-block-driven-themes-with-sketch/music-r2-mobile/\" data-orig-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/music-r2-mobile.png\" data-orig-size=\"375,3089\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Music-R2-Mobile\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/music-r2-mobile.png?w=36\" data-large-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/music-r2-mobile.png?w=124\" /></a>\n<a href=\'https://themeshaper.com/2018/03/07/designing-gutenberg-block-driven-themes-with-sketch/music-r2-desktop/\'><img width=\"50\" height=\"150\" src=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/music-r2-desktop.png?w=50&#038;h=150\" class=\"attachment-thumbnail size-thumbnail\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/music-r2-desktop.png?w=50 50w, https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/music-r2-desktop.png?w=100 100w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 50px) 85vw, 50px\" data-attachment-id=\"7023\" data-permalink=\"https://themeshaper.com/2018/03/07/designing-gutenberg-block-driven-themes-with-sketch/music-r2-desktop/\" data-orig-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/music-r2-desktop.png\" data-orig-size=\"1020,3089\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Music-R2-Desktop\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/music-r2-desktop.png?w=99\" data-large-file=\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/music-r2-desktop.png?w=338\" /></a>\n</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight:400;\">This was a fun exercise, and it helped allay my fears a bit. That first Cover Image has all the usual pieces, but they&#8217;re styled in a very opinionated way. The rest of the blocks are fairly standard, but they still stand out because they exist within a heavily stylized, off-balance frame. The overall effect is drastically different from the theme in the previous exercise. </span></p>\n<hr />\n<p>This process was very useful for me, and I’d love to see if it’s useful for the rest of the community as well. You can download and contribute to the Sketch files here:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/Automattic/gutenberg-themes-sketch\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://github.com/Automattic/gutenberg-themes-sketch</a></p>\n<p>The repository includes a basic Sketch file with just the symbols, plus all the text hierarchy styles (H1, H2, etc). I also created a <a href=\"https://sketchapp.com/docs/libraries/\">library</a> file in case that’s preferable for anyone. We hope to update these files periodically, and would love to hear feedback from others who use them.</p>\n<p>In the meantime, we&#8217;ll keep experimenting with ways to design themes in this new Gutenberg-based future.</p>\n<div><a href=\"https://themeshaper.com/2018/03/07/designing-gutenberg-block-driven-themes-with-sketch/\"><img alt=\"Gutenberg-Sketch-Layout\" src=\"https://videos.files.wordpress.com/3J8YCbg5/gutenberg-sketch-layout_std.original.jpg\" width=\"160\" height=\"120\" /></a></div><div><a href=\"https://themeshaper.com/2018/03/07/designing-gutenberg-block-driven-themes-with-sketch/\"><img alt=\"Gutenberg-Sketch-Customize\" src=\"https://videos.files.wordpress.com/Uu1HxLuE/gutenberg-sketch-customize_std.original.jpg\" width=\"160\" height=\"120\" /></a></div>\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:92:\"https://themeshaper.com/2018/03/07/designing-gutenberg-block-driven-themes-with-sketch/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"5\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:3:{s:9:\"thumbnail\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:3:\"url\";s:88:\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/gutenberg-sketch-file-featured-image.jpg\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:7:\"content\";a:11:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"\n			\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:2:{s:3:\"url\";s:88:\"https://themeshaper.files.wordpress.com/2018/03/gutenberg-sketch-file-featured-image.jpg\";s:6:\"medium\";s:5:\"image\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:1:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:36:\"Gutenberg-Sketch-File-FEATURED-IMAGE\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"html\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:7:\"\n			\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:2:{s:3:\"url\";s:83:\"https://1.gravatar.com/avatar/115aabd707fe985c79744d3e7df8fade?s=96&d=identicon&r=G\";s:6:\"medium\";s:5:\"image\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:1:{s:29:\"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/\";a:1:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:13:\"kjellreigstad\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:1:{s:0:\"\";a:1:{s:4:\"type\";s:4:\"html\";}}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0: